<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1152.98258.figure14>
    dc:description "Figure 14. Photographs of live animals of the genus Sclerodoris Eliot, 1904 A Sclerodoris tuberculata Eliot, 1904, MNHN IM- 2013 - 86197 on black background B-D \" Sclerodoris \" Sclerodoris dutertrei sp. nov., Holotype (MNHN IM- 2013 - 86193) on black background (B), MNHN IM- 2013 - 86195 on black background (C), MNHN IM- 2013 - 86194 on black background (D) E Sclerodoris faninozi sp. nov., Holotype (MNHN IM- 2013 - 86198) on black background." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/820842" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1152.98258.figure15>
    dc:description "Figure 15. Drawing of the reproductive system of specimens of the genus Sclerodoris Eliot, 1904 A-C Sclerodoris tuberculata Eliot, 1904, MNHN IM- 2013 - 86197, general view (A), detail of the bursa copulatrix and seminal receptable (B), penial spines (C) D-F Sclerodoris faninozi sp. nov., Holotype (MNHN IM- 2013 - 86198), general view (D), detail of the bursa copulatrix and seminal receptable (E), penial spines (F) G \" Sclerodoris \" Sclerodoris dutertrei sp. nov., MNHN IM- 2013 - 86193. Abbreviations: ag, accessory gland; am, ampulla; bc, bursa copulatrix; dd, deferent duct; fg, female gland complex; pr, prostate; sr, seminal receptacle; vg, vagina." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/820843" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1152.98258.figure16>
    dc:description "Figure 16. SEM of the radula of specimens of the genus Sclerodoris Eliot, 1904 A-C Sclerodoris tuberculata Eliot, 1904, MNHN IM- 2013 - 86197, innermost teeth (A), mid-lateral teeth (B), outer lateral teeth (C) D-F \" Sclerodoris \" Sclerodoris dutertrei sp. nov., MNHN IM- 2013 - 86195, innermost teeth (D), mid-lateral teeth (E), outer lateral teeth (F) G-I Sclerodoris faninozi sp. nov., Holotype (MNHN IM- 2013 - 86198), innermost teeth (G), mid-lateral teeth (H), outer lateral teeth (I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/820844" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

